<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<title>yạ rạwyny yạ yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (yạ rạwyny yạ yswʿ bḥnạnk .. ḥyạty hy rḍạk
 ạ̹nt yạ rby frḥẗ qlby .. ạ̉nạ ʿạysẖ hnạ bạstnạk)2
 yạ rạfʿ rạsy fy ạlḍyq .. yạ mjdy yạ ạ̉gẖly̱ ṣdyq
 yạ ḥbyby yạ mạly ḥyạty .. yạ fạdyã yswʿ mạ ạ̉ḥlạk
 (hllwyạ hllwyạ .. qlby tẖạbt wạ̉nạ wyạk
 hllwyạ hllwyạ .. ạ̉nạ lyã mkạn fy smạk)2</lyrics>
</song>